{"tid":1576592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［整理］831太子站消防文件時間線","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T08:37:39.000Z","uid":217635,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"4464e0b6f5d660d256ffba224e94b12876485959","tid":1576592,"uid":217635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">23:05:32 <br />\n事件發生<br />\n4架消防車 1架救護車<br />\n十多名消防員到達太子站<br />\n<br />\n正常情況下消防冇發現火災但發現傷者<br />\n係應該回到車上攞急救工具 再落去月台 <br />\n(Log冇記錄呢一點)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Log Date Time 時間線</span></ins><br />\n23:43:52<br />\n消防員在場點算傷者<br />\n<br />\n23:46:37<br />\n已知<span style=\"color: gold;\">3名傷者</span> (1女 2男)<br />\n消防車通知控制中心需要五個救護人員去到太子站，整體估計10-15名傷者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n23:49:59 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3名傷者</span> (1氣促 2頭部受傷)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n23:54:42<br />\n分流決定：3G/Y 廣華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:01:31  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">9名傷者</span> (頭、氣促、腳)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:15:13<br />\n太子E出口 警察稱月台冇傷者，<br />\n不容許救護員進入<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">疑點：消防可以出入拎工具，<br />\n但唔允許救護員進入？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:15:23  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">10名傷者 </span>(6R2Y2G)<br />\n需要7架救護車 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:20:49<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">9名傷者</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點：根據000131、001523、002049嘅三次匯報，可確定至少9-10名傷者 <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:20:52<br />\n分流決定：<br />\n2R 廣華、2R QE、1R 明愛<br />\n1R 瑪嘉烈、1Y1G 廣華、1Y1G QE<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總共10名傷者</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:22:12 <br />\n醫管局+醫院前線回覆 <span style=\"color: red;\">確認10名傷者嘅分流</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:25:21 <br />\nMTR稱確認月台已清場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:26:59 <br />\n救護員進入太子站增援<br />\n直至01:02:24都冇匯報<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">疑點：期間不論有冇發現傷者 都應該匯報<br />\n但呢段時間空白咗</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:02:24  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">7名傷者</span> (3R2Y2G)<br />\n此訊息由荔景流動指揮車基於見習救護主任所述發出<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">疑點：見習救護主任可以直接匯報<br />\n為何隔咗一個荔景指揮</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:07:48  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">10/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n救護高級主任引述高級警司稱<br />\n7名傷者將會送去荔枝角站<br />\n需要五架救護車準備<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">疑點：<br />\n救援行動應以救護親眼確認<br />\n不應引述其他部門所述</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:10:48  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n醫管局改變分流決定<br />\n1R1G1Y 明愛<br />\n2R1G1Y 瑪嘉烈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:16:46  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">10/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n需要多一架救護車喺荔枝角stand by <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:39:43  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n13個救護人員到場 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:44:30  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">10/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n高級警司指示將7名傷者送去荔枝角站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01:55:43  <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3/9 竄改</span></span><br />\n7名傷者到達地面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會直播：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JoQ-Jly_hYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJoQ-Jly_hYY&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=af0d18de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JoQ-Jly_hYY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(可能有少少亂，有錯或有補充請指出)</span>"},{"pid":"c8a749dc4d245f239078a2567abea5da532316f6","tid":1576592,"uid":217635,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"打時間線出嚟希望幫到大家分析件事